com.mostc.pftt.scenario
Class Scenario

java.lang.Object
  com.mostc.pftt.scenario.Scenario
Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractParallelScenario, AbstractSerialScenario, SuhosinScenario
public abstract class Scenario
extends java.lang.Object

Scenario to test PHP under. Often a whole set of Scenarios (@see ScenarioSet) are used together. May include custom INI configuration, extensions, environment variables, etc... Can be used to setup remote services and configure PHP to use them for testing PHP core or extensions.

Author:
Matt Ficken
See Also:
Important Scenario Types, - provides the SAPI that a PhpBuild is run under (Apache-ModPHP, CLI, etc...), - edits/adds to the INI used to run a PhptTestCase, - provides the filesystem a PhpBuild is run on (local, remote, etc...)
